fulltitle: The Maestros of Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 – La cumparsita
title: The Maestros of Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 – La cumparsita
_filename: The Maestros of Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 – La cumparsita-pElmvD84O3c.mp4
description:
The Maestros of the Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 dance “La cumparsita” played live by Solo Tango Orquesta.

The Maestros are
Mariana Montes and Sebastián Arce
Yanina Quiñones and Neri Piliu
Mariela Sametband and Guille Barrionuevo
Sara Grdan and Ivan Terrazas
Iris Başak Doğdu and Utku Küley
Georgia Priskou and Loukas Balokas
Sonja Schüssler and Özgür Arin
